</ol>
<p><b><span data-contrast="none">Om </span></b><b><span data-contrast="none">Brilliant Awards – </span></b><b><span data-contrast="none">Customer</span></b><b><span data-contrast="none"> </span></b><b><span data-contrast="none">Experience</span></b><b><span data-contrast="none"> – “<a href="https://www.brilliantfuture.se/customer-experience-award/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Bästa kundservice</a>”:</span></b><span data-ccp-props="{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559740&quot;:276}"> </span></p>
<ul>
<li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="1" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><span data-contrast="none">Listar de företag som har lyckats skapa exceptionella kundupplevelser.</span><span data-ccp-props="{&quot;134233279&quot;:true,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559740&quot;:240}"> </span></li>
